lucy kate jackson ( born october 29 , 1948 ) is an american actress , director and producer , known for her television roles as sabrina duncan in the 1970s series charlie 's angels ( 1976–79 ) and amanda king in the 1980s series scarecrow and mrs. king ( 1983–87 ) .

